    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096480/extras/80b81ffa0add6ff7c07d63b7a59b3261.poster.avif?t=1664686239\" width=638 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096480/extras/80b81ffa0add6ff7c07d63b7a59b3261.webm?t=1664686239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096480/extras/80b81ffa0add6ff7c07d63b7a59b3261.mp4?t=1664686239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>破碎之星是一个结合了割草跟肉鸽题材的独立小游戏。游戏系统提供了大量武器跟强化选择。让玩家可以尝试和选择不同的组合来更快的斩杀敌人。我们没有故事线，因为只有3个半职开发者QAQ。你不需要知道你是谁你在哪，你只用知道你需要嘎嘎乱杀 :) 我们提供了‘是男人就过30层’跟‘生存下去’两个模式，会根据玩家反馈对游戏模式进行更多的打磨。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096480/extras/c5fb72cba9f78d8d2223cfb773ad2050.poster.avif?t=1664686239\" width=638 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096480/extras/c5fb72cba9f78d8d2223cfb773ad2050.webm?t=1664686239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096480/extras/c5fb72cba9f78d8d2223cfb773ad2050.mp4?t=1664686239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>我们添加了一个特殊的‘祝福’系统，玩家可以通过对武器添加‘祝福’来使武器拥有一个额外的强大技能，这个强大的技能需要通过满足特定条件进行触发。这个‘祝福’系统大幅度添加了游戏的多样性。每次游戏几乎不可能出现完全一样的组合因为‘祝福’的触发条件是完全随机生成的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096480/extras/38adf818789a782dacba1256723fb216.poster.avif?t=1664686239\" width=640 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096480/extras/38adf818789a782dacba1256723fb216.webm?t=1664686239\" type=\"video/webm; c